Invocation Name: quiz me
des: Quiz Me skill is basically developed to play a fun trivia quiz game that would ask for fun and informative questions from all the fields like science, technology, music, movies, sports, space, etc. The skills are designed for any category of the user from small children to matured people. It is a fun game and a proper skill to help you pass time wth Alexa.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
